OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1782195489
OL,3,CMet Office issues red warning for
OL,4,Crecord-breaking heatwave of up to 40C
OL,6,FA rare extreme heat warning has been
OL,7,Fissued for parts of southern England
OL,8,Fand Wales as temperatures are expected
OL,9,Fto reach up to 40C this week.
OL,11,FThe Met Office has issued a red
OL,12,Fwarning - the highest level of alert -
OL,13,Fmeaning there is a risk to life for
OL,14,Feveryone in the heat, not just those
OL,15,Fconsidered vulnerable.
OL,17,FIt begins on Wednesday at 9am and ends
OL,18,FThursday 9pm, and covers Birmingham,
OL,19,FSalisbury, Swansea and London.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
