OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1782195489
OL,3,CMet Office issues red warning for
OL,4,Crecord-breaking heatwave of up to 40C
OL,6,F"You may need to gently use your hands
OL,7,Fto help you stay afloat, and it's ok
OL,8,Fif your legs sink`everyone floats
OL,9,Fdifferently."
OL,11,FThe heatwave in the UK is also being
OL,12,Ffelt in Europe due to a 'heat dome',
OL,13,Fwhich occurs when high pressure
OL,14,Fremains stuck over a large area,
OL,15,Ftrapping hot air beneath it.
OL,17,FMore than half of France has been
OL,18,Fplaced under a red heat alert, with
OL,19,Ftemperatures of up to 43C expected in
OL,20,Fparts of the country and many schools
OL,21,Fdeciding to close on Monday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1782195489
OL,3,CMet Office issues red warning for
OL,4,Crecord-breaking heatwave of up to 40C
OL,6,FMedical specialists have warned of the
OL,7,Fpotentially deadly cocktail of
OL,8,Fdrinking alcohol in extreme heat and
OL,9,Fauthorities are cracking down on
OL,10,Falcohol consumption in public.
OL,12,FItaly has also issued heatwave
OL,13,Fwarnings in eight cities, while
OL,14,FSpain's Basque Country, in the north,
OL,15,Fcancelled multiple sports and cultural
OL,16,Fevents.
OL,18,FThe World Health Organisation said
OL,19,Fover 200,000 people in Europe have
OL,20,Fdied from heat-related causes in the
OL,21,Fpast four years.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
